{
  "stem": "22447.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then a few hours later, an order comes through, the beaches are out of bounds to all ranks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Before, they used to tell you to while away your time, go swimming in the sea or whatever, but it was out of bounds for all ranks.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So in a certain way, the word's coming up, well, what's going on?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So it turns out that the Germans, they had all these barges.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They filled them up with troops, and they did launch an invasion against the Isle of Wight, but how do you get the barges across the channel?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Barges can't go by themselves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They got the Italian navy, [INAUDIBLE] torpedo boats, to tow them across the channel but the rope towing them was behind the barge.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the idea was when they come about a mile offshore, they part, the two barges part, catapulting the barge into the Isle of Wight.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the speed of that would've been between 50 to 60 miles an hour.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if they come in like that, there was nothing-- you could stop them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had nothing to stop them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All we had was a rifle and 15 rounds of ammunition, nothing else.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was no anti-tank guns, anything, nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Just 15 rounds of ammunition, that's all we had.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had a stretch of beach, nine miles, I think it was from Ventnor to St.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Catherine's Point, the whole length of the beach there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the idea was, when they part they catapult these barges in.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
